    "verification_notes": "Corrections: (1) Omumwa→Salt was WRONG — Omumwa=Mouth. Corrected to Omunnyo=Salt. (2) Kaawa (Coffee) appeared twice — duplicate removed. (3) Jiko→Spoon was WRONG — Jiko=charcoal stove. Corrected to Ekijiko=Spoon. (4) Ebirabo→Restaurant was WRONG — Ebirabo=gifts. Corrected to Ootteli/Reesituraanti. (5) Okulyia misspelling corrected to Okulya. (6) Omucungwa corrected from 'Orange Juice' to 'Orange (fruit)'. (7) Enva clarified from 'Sauce/Vegetables' to 'Relish/Side sauce'. (8) Ebirala (Others) removed — too vague, not food-specific. (9) Okuwaata flagged for spelling review."
